1. 9 routes:
	comments#create
	comments#destroy
	treasures#index
	treasures#show
	treasures#new
	treasures#edit
	treasures#create
	treasures#update
	treasures#destroy

2. 2 models:
	"comments", "treasures"

3. 3 controllers:
	application, comments, treasures

4. CRUD logic takes place in the controllers.

5. app/treasures/new.html.erb allows us to create a new treasure

6. app/treasures/show.html.erb allows us to comment on an existing feature

7. app/treasures/index.html.erb is our home page

8. app/treasures/index.html.erb lists all the treasures

9. 	Treasure attributes: title, description, created_at && updated_at timestamps
	Comments attributes: bru, comment, treasure_id, created_at && updated_at timestamps

10. config/db/schema.rb displays the attributes for each model